Package: cropZoning
Type: Package
Title: Climate crop zoning for the most common crops of Brazil with
        TerraClimate dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Roberto Filgueiras [aut, cre] (<https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Roberto_Filgueiras>),
        Luan Peroni Venancio (<https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Luan_Venancio>),
        Catariny Cabral Aleman (<https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Catariny_Aleman>),
        Fernando Fran<e7>a da Cunha (<https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Fernando_Cunha16>),
Maintainer: Roberto Filgueiras <betofilgueiras@gmail.com>
Description: cropZoning uses minimum and maximum air temperature data from TerraClimate dataset (http://www.climatologylab.org/terraclimate.html) to make climate zoning of different crops (air temperature based) for Brazilian territory.
